ActBusiness Development Bank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of VALERIE A. PAYN of Bedford, Nova Scotia, in the place of Jennifer Corson, whose term has expired, and LEO LEDOHOWSKI of Winnipeg, Manitoba, in the place of Leo Cholakis, whose term has expired, as directors of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
